\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 Article 1 (Purpose)
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 The purpose of this Act is to provide for matters concerning control over the immigration of all \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
nationals and foreigners who enter or depart from the Republic of Korea, control over the sojourn of foreigners who stay in the Republic of Korea, and the procedure for recognition of refugees. 
\par 
