\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (1) Any foreigner may sojourn in the Republic of Korea within the limit of his status of sojourn and period of sojourn.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (2) No foreigner sojourning in the Republic of Korea shall \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 engage in any political activity.
