 sojourning in the Republic of Korea is engaged in any political activity, the Minister of Justice may order him in writing to suspend such activity or may take other necessary measures.
\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 Article 18 (Restriction on Employment of Foreigners)
