\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (3) No person shall employ any person having no status of sojourn as referred to in paragraph (1).
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (4) No person shall mediate or solicit for any employment of a person having no status of so\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 journ as referred to in paragraph (1).
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (5) No person shall put under his control any foreigner having no status of sojourn as referred to in paragraph (1) with the intention to mediate an employment of such person.
