\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 Article 46 (Persons to be Deported)
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (1) The head of office or branch office or head of a foreigner internment camp may deport any of the\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
 following foreigners from the Republic of Korea according to procedures as prescribed in this Chapter: 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 1.A person who violated the provisions of Article 7;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 1-2.A person who violated the provisions of Article 7-2, or a person who entered the country by th\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 e act such as a false invitation as stipulated in the same Article;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 2.A person who is found to fall under any of subparagraphs of Article 11 (1) after entry;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 3.A person who violated the provisions of Article 12 (1) or (2), or 12-2;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 4.A person who violated \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 the condition imposed by the head of the office or branch office under Article 13 (2);
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 5.A person who landed without obtaining permission as prescribed in Article 14 (1), 15 (1), 16 (1) or 16-2 (1);
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 6. A person who violated the condition imposed by the hea\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 d of an office or branch office or an immigration control official under Article 14 (2), 15 (2), 16 (2) or 16-2 (2);
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 6.A person who violated the condition imposed by the head of an office or branch office or an immigration control official under Article 14\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12  (3), 15 (2), 16 (2) or 16-2 (2);
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 [[Enforcement Date: September 25, 2005]]
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 7.A person who violated the provisions of Article 17 (1) and (2), 18, 20, 21, 23, 24 or 25;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 8.A person who violated a residence restriction, restriction on the scope of activity, or\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12  other matters to be observed, etc. as prescribed by the Minister of Justice under Article 22;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 9.A person who attempted to depart from the Republic of Korea in contravention of Article 28;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 10.A person who violated the provisions of Article 31;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 11.A person \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 who is released after receiving a sentence of punishment of imprisonment without prison labor or heavier punishment; and
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 12. Other persons corresponding to subparagraphs 1 through 11, who are provided by the Ordinance of the Ministry of Justice.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 [[Enforcem\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 ent Date: September 25, 2005]]
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (2) Notwithstanding paragraph (1), any foreigner who holds his sojourn status that entitles him to the permanent residentship in the Republic of Korea from among sojourn statuses provided for in Article 10 (1) shall not be de
\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 ported from the Republic of Korea: Provided, That the same shall not apply to foreigners falling under any of the following subparagraphs: 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 1.Foreigner who has committed the insurrection provided for in Chapter I of Part }{\fs20\insrsid13049738 \loch\af12\hich\af0\dbch\f12 \'a5\'b1}{\fs20\insrsid13049738 \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
 of the Criminal Act or the foreig\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 n aggression provided for in Chapter }{\fs20\insrsid13049738 \loch\af12\hich\af0\dbch\f12 \'a5\'b1}{\fs20\insrsid13049738 \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12  of the same Act;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 2.Foreigner who is prescribed by the Ordinance of the Ministry of Justice from among foreigners who have been released after having been sentenced to imprisonment with prison labor or without prison 
\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 labor for not less than 5 years: and
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 3.Foreigner who has committed a violation of the provisions of Article 12-2 (1) or (2), or has abetted or aided another person in such violation.
