\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 2.A country where he was born;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 3.A country that includes the port at which he boarded s\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 hips, etc. to enter the Republic of Korea; and
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 4.Other country to which he desires to be repatriated.
