\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 e\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12  or part of the guarantee money to the National Treasury.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (3) The procedure for reversion of guarantee money to the National Treasury under paragraph (2) shall be determined by the Presidential Decree.
