) calls at a port in a foreign country due to special circumstances, such as an unforeseen accident, problems on navigation, etc., they shall, upon entering thereafter a port of the Republic of Korea, undergo an entry search\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
 conducted by the immigration control official under Chapters 7 and 8.
