\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (1) If the crew and passengers of the ships, etc. being moored at an immigration port or place other than the\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
 immigration port, or any person other than those permitted to enter pursuant to the provisions of other Acts and subordinate statutes, desire to enter the ships, etc., they shall obtain the permission of the head of office or branch office on the embarka
\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 t\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 ion.
