\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 2.Time of reservation and boarding process;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 3.Travel route and travel agency;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 4.Accompanied passenger and seat number;
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 5.Luggage; and
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 6.Settlement method of Price for purchasing air tickets.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 [[\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 Enforcement Date: September 25, 2005]]
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (4) The immigration control official capable of perusing the data or of requesting to submit them in writing under paragraph (2) shall be limited to the persons designated by the head of office or branch office. 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 [[En\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 forcement Date: September 25, 2005]]
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (5) The immigration control official designated under paragraph (4) shall not use the data of reservation information systems known to him on duties for unlawful purposes, such as divulging, or disposing of without any 
\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 authority, or providing for use by others. 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 [[Enforcement Date: September 25, 2005]]
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (6) The detailed matters on the perusal method and preservation period, etc. of the data under paragraph (2) shall be prescribed by the Presidential Decree. 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 [[Enforcement\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12  Date: September 25, 2005]]
