or other places, is informed that a person who does not hold a passport (in case of sailors. it refers to a passport and seaman's identification papers) is aboard the ships, etc., he shall report such fact without delay to the head of office or branch off
\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 i\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 ce and prevent the person from landing. 
