\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 Article 76-2 (\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 Recognition of Refugees)
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
(1) When the Minister of Justice receives a request for recognition of refugee status from a foreigner staying in the Republic of Korea under the conditions as prescribed by the Presidential Decree, he may recognize the foreigner a
\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 s a refugee.
