(2) The request as referred to in paragraph (1) shall be made within one year after the foreigner lands or enters the Republic of Korea (if a cause to be a refugee occurs during his sojourn in the Republic of Korea, the day on which he knows t
\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 he fact), except in case where he is ill, or there is any inevitable reason. 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (3) When the Minister of Justice has recognized a foreigner as a refugee under paragraph (1), he shall deliver a refugee recognition certificate to the foreigner, and if not, not\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
ify him of the reason in writing.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (4) The procedure of examination on a recognition of refugee under paragraph (1), and other necessary matters, shall be determined by the Presidential Decree.
