\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (1) With respect to any offense regarding immigration, no public action shall be instituted \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
without an accusation of the head of office or branch office or the head of the foreigner internment camp. 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (2) If a criminal investigation agency other than the immigration control official has booked for any case falling under the text of paragraph (1), \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
it shall without delay hand the case over to the head of office or branch office or the head of the foreigner internment camp.
\par 
