\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (1) When an immigration offender has a written notice served, he shall pay the penalty within ten days. 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 (2) If the immigration offender fails to pay the penalty within the period as \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 
