\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 Article 106 (Prohibition against Double Jeopardy)
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 When an immigration offender has paid the penalty as noticed, he shall not be pun\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f12 ished for the same violation.
